<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 18:08:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“我向加沙开火”：以色列军队用复仇诗歌鼓励士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/send-fire-on-gaza-israels-army-uses-revenge-poetry-to-encourage-its-soldiers/0000018e-7bad-d96c-af9f-7fed4ee60000</link><description>以色列国防军出版的一本选集包含表达复仇欲望的诗歌，并将加沙的战斗描绘成一场宗教战争。这促使一些人质疑文学倡议是否违反了军队自身的价值观</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:53:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/send-fire-on-gaza-israels-army-uses-revenge-poetry-to-encourage-its-soldiers/0000018e-7bad-d96c-af9f-7fed4ee60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 172 天：以色列消息人士称，人质释放谈判“并未破裂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-172-hostage-release-talks-have-not-collapsed-says-israeli-source/0000018e-7bae-d8a5-addf-7bbf6a0c0001</link><description>哈马斯拒绝美国释放人质/停火的提议 ■ 部分以色列代表团仍留在卡塔尔继续谈判 ■ 红新月会：以色列国防军撤离并封锁了汗尤尼斯的阿迈勒医院入口 ■ 联合国人权问题特别报告员：以色列在加沙的行动相当于种族灭绝 ■ 美国高级官员在与国防部长加兰特的会晤中寻求缓解美以紧张局势 ■ 战争结束 172 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-172-hostage-release-talks-have-not-collapsed-says-israeli-source/0000018e-7bae-d8a5-addf-7bbf6a0c0001</guid></item><item><title>戈兰高地热门咖啡馆因北部战争永久关门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/popular-golan-heights-cafe-permanently-closes-doors-due-to-war-in-north/0000018e-7b8a-d8a5-addf-7bbba3460000</link><description>Coffee Anan 是一家位于戈兰高地风景秀丽的本塔尔山的咖啡馆，在以色列国防军宣布以色列北部大部分地区为军事禁区后，该咖啡馆宣布关闭。咖啡馆的名字是前联合国秘书长科菲·安南和希伯来语“云”一词的组合</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/popular-golan-heights-cafe-permanently-closes-doors-due-to-war-in-north/0000018e-7b8a-d8a5-addf-7bbba3460000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列军事指挥官警告该法案草案将损害国家安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-military-commanders-warn-draft-bill-would-damage-national-security/0000018e-7b7e-d9f5-a7ae-7f7f972d0000</link><description>在向该国领导人发出的请求中，指挥官们警告不要大幅增加预备役军人服役，同时免除极端正统派人士的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-military-commanders-warn-draft-bill-would-damage-national-security/0000018e-7b7e-d9f5-a7ae-7f7f972d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列令人不安地否认加沙遭受饥饿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/inside-israels-disturbing-denial-of-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-7b41-d680-a1cf-ff47b4220000</link><description>以色列当局和亲以色列的键盘侠系统地否认专家研究、援助机构和加沙人自己关于加沙灾难性饥饿的证据，他们有明确的、无耻的动机</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/inside-israels-disturbing-denial-of-starvation-in-gaza/0000018e-7b41-d680-a1cf-ff47b4220000</guid></item><item><title>莫斯科袭击事件后，俄罗斯新的影响力运动试图用草率的希伯来语将责任归咎于西方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/after-moscow-attack-new-russian-campaign-tries-to-pin-blame-on-west-in-sloppy-hebrew/0000018e-7b63-d96c-af9f-7fe353570000</link><description>莫斯科袭击事件导致至少 139 人死亡，之后以色列社交媒体上出现了数千个账户，并将责任归咎于乌克兰和西方国家。在寻求以色列对恐怖袭击受害者的同情时，该活动的草率希伯来语导致了嘲笑和失败</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/after-moscow-attack-new-russian-campaign-tries-to-pin-blame-on-west-in-sloppy-hebrew/0000018e-7b63-d96c-af9f-7fe353570000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权利组织在耶路撒冷普珥节街头派对上散发传单，抗议以色列在加沙的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/group-drops-leaflets-on-purim-street-party-in-jerusalem-protesting-israeli-action-in-gaza/0000018e-7b63-d946-a3ff-7fe7e8980000</link><description>在该组织的 X 帐户上发布的一段视频中，传单在空中漂浮，然后落在普珥节聚会参与者的脚下。传单上用希伯来语写道：“自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列军队已造成 32,000 人死亡。” “超过一百万人处于危险之中。停止屠杀”</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 16:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/group-drops-leaflets-on-purim-street-party-in-jerusalem-protesting-israeli-action-in-gaza/0000018e-7b63-d946-a3ff-7fe7e8980000</guid></item><item><title>1300万美元现金从哥伦比亚购买一架私人飞机：对以色列国防出口主管来说不是问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/13m-cash-on-a-private-jet-from-colombia-a-nonissue-for-israeli-head-of-defense-export/0000018e-7689-d706-a39f-f7f93fa10000</link><description>国防部出口援助部门负责人亚伊尔·库拉斯参与了令人惊讶的交易。但本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的新政府拯救了他</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 14:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/13m-cash-on-a-private-jet-from-colombia-a-nonissue-for-israeli-head-of-defense-export/0000018e-7689-d706-a39f-f7f93fa10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列不是攻击拉法，而是内塔尼亚胡攻击华盛顿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-israel-attacking-rafah-netanyahu-attacks-washington/0000018e-79e1-d96c-af9f-7fe1f12d0000</link><description>总理本可以通过多种方式表达对联合国安理会决议的不满，但他选择了最糟糕的一种：发动外交攻击，为哈马斯辛瓦尔和真主党服务，并损害将人质带回家的努力</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 12:56:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-israel-attacking-rafah-netanyahu-attacks-washington/0000018e-79e1-d96c-af9f-7fe1f12d0000</guid></item><i