, 26 Mar 2024 09:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/saharan-desert-warbler-spotted-in-haifa-thousands-of-miles-from-home/0000018e-7a08-d96c-af9f-7ec9b4510000</guid></item><item><title>国防官员担心：比比-拜登的口角可能对美以关系造成持久损害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-bibi-biden-spat-could-do-lasting-harm-to-u-s-israel-ties/0000018e-7743-dac2-a3de-7ffb86f90000</link><description>以色列总理的威胁没有给美国总统留下任何印象——他已经失去了耐心。美国人不明白内塔尼亚胡想要什么，但从以色列的角度来看，答案很明确：不惜一切代价保住权力</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 04:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-bibi-biden-spat-could-do-lasting-harm-to-u-s-israel-ties/0000018e-7743-dac2-a3de-7ffb86f90000</guid></item><item><title>第二个巴勒斯坦难民问题的诞生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/the-birth-of-a-second-palestinian-refugee-problem/0000018e-7660-d680-a1cf-fe67d0770000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡现在必须决定是否将以色列人质带回家并允许加沙北部居民返回——即使以他的执政联盟出现裂痕为代价——还是加入极右翼并宣布创建“巴勒斯坦难民”问题2&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 04:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article/.premium/the-birth-of-a-second-palestinian-refugee-problem/0000018e-7660-d680-a1cf-fe67d0770000</guid></item><item><title>数十枚火箭弹向以色列北部发射；以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩深处的真主党目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-in-cease-fire-talks-with-israel/0000018e-78b4-d8a5-addf-78b7e61c0000</link><description>部分以色列代表团仍留在卡塔尔，进行人质释放/停火谈判 ■ 汗尤尼斯 Al-Amal 医院撤离的报告 ■ 拉法的报道：18 人在袭击住宅的罢工中丧生 ■ 美国官员表示希望缓和美国与美国之间的紧张局势以色列 ■ 哈马斯领导人哈尼亚前往德黑兰与伊朗官员会面</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-26/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-mediators-it-will-stick-to-original-position-in-cease-fire-talks-with-israel/0000018e-78b4-d8a5-addf-78b7e61c0000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝活动和抗议活动成为耶路撒冷普珥节游行的焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/celebrations-protests-take-center-stage-at-jerusalems-purim-parade/0000018e-776d-d8a5-addf-77ff327d0000</link><description>“我们正在使战争正常化。世界将如何看待这一点，”抗议者尼尔·阿尔戈夫说。 “十五万名撤离者无法盛装打扮或庆祝，首都却举办一场盛大的聚会”</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 21:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/celebrations-protests-take-center-stage-at-jerusalems-purim-parade/0000018e-776d-d8a5-addf-77ff327d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不将吉迪恩·萨尔纳入战时内阁后，吉迪恩·萨尔退出联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/gideon-saar-quits-coalition-after-netanyahu-doesnt-include-him-in-war-cabinet/0000018e-7745-d8a5-addf-77f7264f0000</link><description>萨尔说，他在安全内阁中多次表达了这些观点，但没有效果，因为该论坛已成为一个空谈场所，所有重要决定都是由战时内阁做出的</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 20:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/gideon-saar-quits-coalition-after-netanyahu-doesnt-include-him-in-war-cabinet/0000018e-7745-d8a5-addf-77f7264f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡让以色列走上了与美国发生冲突的道路。联合国停火投票是可怕的结果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-put-israel-on-a-collision-course-with-america-the-un-vote-is-the-result/0000018e-76eb-d616-a7ee-feeb520a0000</link><description>自去年11月以来，我们多次撰文表示这种情况将会发生，美国也不断警告以色列这种情况很可能发生。以色列无视这些威胁，现在不诚实地假装惊讶和震惊</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 19:49:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-put-israel-on-a-collision-course-with-america-the-un-vote-is-the-result/0000018e-76eb-d616-a7ee-feeb520a0000</guid></item><item><title>这位非犹太同性恋喜剧演员如何成为以色列最热情的倡导者之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-this-non-jewish-gay-comedian-became-one-of-israels-most-passionate-advocates/0000018e-762b-d96c-af9f-7eeb69a80000</link><description>过去，出生于加拿大的丹尼尔-瑞安·斯波尔丁甚至不确定自己在以色列表演是否舒服。自 10 月 7 日袭击以来，他已成为网上最知名的以色列捍卫者和哈马斯攻击者之一。但甚至不要让他开始柏林</description><pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 19:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-this-non-jewish-gay-comedian-became-one-of-israels-most-passionate-advocates/0000018e-762b-d96c-af9f-7eeb69a80000</guid></item></channel></rss>